  "detailed_description": "This is a survival and leisure Roguelike game, where monsters will constantly invade and make their characters stronger through repeated choices! Easy to operate, just control the protagonist's movement to engage in combat.<br />\r\nThe gold coins collected in the battle can permanently strengthen the protagonist and unlock new heroes!<br />\r\nYou can use a mouse, keyboard, joystick, or touch screen for control!",
